Abstract:
    (Data Hiding)
 =>There is no implimentasion,only declarision
     
Encapsulation:
	(Binding Data & Method as one Entity)
=>Binding a Data Using Setters & Getters

Inheritance:
	(code Reusability)	
=>Allows us to create a new class from an existing class	  

Polymorphism:
	( Object Act like many forms)   
=>Reusing the Functionality And Adding new Feature	